{"title":"洋葱","authors":["野村由纪子"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"洋葱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔日本〕　野村由纪子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我要买洋葱！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想把手伸出去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞬间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又制止了自己的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为：映入我眼帘的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是日本自己的洋葱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那种洋葱，身长头尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用大红和粉红色的袋子装饰着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装在写着英文字母的结实木箱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从美国运来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在日本各地销售。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“便宜一元也是好的！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不知谁这么说道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“便宜，便宜，把日本的农业挤垮了那是不能宽恕的。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——别人顶了他一声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从日美“安全条约”生效以来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强加在日本民族身上的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不尽的屈辱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军事基地、核潜艇、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Ｆ105Ｄ型飞机、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴行、屠杀、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香蕉、面粉、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱脂奶粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呸！够了，真够多了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，今天又运来了洋葱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种植着洋葱的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们日本的农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日益走向破产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目击这种情景的日本人的我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么可以吃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由沾满人民鲜血的双手推销过来的洋葱呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧着吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会向那双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啐上唾沫的！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我默默地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深吸了一口气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我要买这个……”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把手伸向那洋葱旁边的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本自己种的蔬菜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔谢冬译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}